description = """
Automated Quantum Mechanical Environments (AQME) offers transparent and
reproducible workflows available for Jupyter Notebooks and command lines,
including:
1) RDKit- and CREST-based conformer generation,
2) QM input file creation,
3) post-processing of QM output files,
4) generation of xTB, DFT and RDKit descriptors.
"""

